  "title": "复盘",
  "content": "<div class=\"rich_media_content js_underline_content defaultNoSetting\" id=\"js_content\">\n <section>\n  <span leaf=\"\">\n   昨天看到个统计数字\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <span leaf=\"\">\n   说上半年全市场共有135支个\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <span leaf=\"\">\n   股实现翻倍级的涨幅\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <span leaf=\"\">\n   属实是不算少的\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <span leaf=\"\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <span leaf=\"\">\n   那么那些专业的顶流基金经理人\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <span leaf=\"\">\n   讲道理业绩会更为靓丽\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <span leaf=\"\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <span leaf=\"\">\n   我们来看一下顶流基金经理人\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <span leaf=\"\">\n   在2025年过去半年内的表现：\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <span leaf=\"\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <span leaf=\"\">\n   刘彦春的\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <span leaf=\"\">\n   景顺长城新兴成长混合\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <span leaf=\"\">\n   近六个月来的表现为：\n   <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\" textstyle=\"\">\n    -4.98%\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </section>\n <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n  <span leaf=\"\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <section>\n  <span leaf=\"\">\n   张坤的\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <span leaf=\"\">\n   易方达蓝筹精选混合\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <span leaf=\"\">\n   近六个月来的表现为：+0.83%\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <span leaf=\"\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <span leaf=\"\">\n   朱少醒\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <span leaf=\"\">\n   富国天惠成长混合\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <span leaf=\"\">\n   近六个月来的表现为：+0.67%\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <span leaf=\"\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <span leaf=\"\">\n   谢治宇\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <span leaf=\"\">\n   兴全合润混合\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <span leaf=\"\">\n   近六个月来的表现为：+3.63%\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <span leaf=\"\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <span leaf=\"\">\n   而这也就是主动权益类基金的现状\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <span leaf=\"\">\n   即一个个堪称中国巴菲特\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <span leaf=\"\">\n   的上半年的业绩表现\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <span leaf=\"\">\n   甚至跑不赢银行利息的收益\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <span leaf=\"\">\n   那么就比如上半年亏了-4.98%\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <span leaf=\"\">\n   跑输大盘的刘彦春\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <span leaf=\"\">\n   他是水平不行么？\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <span leaf=\"\">\n   当然不是，人家可是名副其实的顶流\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <span leaf=\"\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <span leaf=\"\">\n   所以空仓会错过什么？\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <span leaf=\"\">\n   空仓什么也没有错过\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <span leaf=\"\">\n   我身边也有坚持在场的\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <span leaf=\"\">\n   闹腾了半年的所谓牛市\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <span leaf=\"\">\n   打个平手的就算很不错了\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <span leaf=\"\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <span leaf=\"\">\n   近日证监会更换了其标志\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <span leaf=\"\">\n   把原先三个连环套的标志\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\n  <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"503829530\" data-ratio=\"1.0392441860465116\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"688\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/JTOJib7cBANuyCXevic0GOI0MHXTAKGQqUFHyiaUA51vicFjZPHwKsI5doPrbUBH5QafxE7dWyNiaiclzcODFc0f29Cw/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" style=\"width: 1080px;height:253px;\" type=\"block\"/>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <span leaf=\"\">\n   替换成了三个V字：\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\n  <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"503829529\" data-ratio=\"0.9041353383458647\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-ty